{"tid":1364100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗美食及購物指南","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T12:05:00.000Z","uid":16740,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"9782ed0ba69bc4110e1b6faa06eabe5a49fb14a0","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"作為一個係元朗土生土長既牛屎仔<br />\n今日想推廣一下元朗既好去處，美食及購物地點<br />\n<br />\n首先，中秋即將來臨，相信好多香港人都想食到好食既月餅，小弟現推介恆香月餅，恆香既月餅比市面上既好好多，好有月餅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟最高紀錄一次過食撚左兩盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />地址係元朗大棠路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhEy3fF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqhEy3fF.png&h=6553412f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二間就係元朗人必食既爽爽醉雞豬扒店，一定要食新鮮雞！好撚滑！豬扒又係好撚有豬扒味，諗起都想食番一打<br />\n地址係YOHO 附近<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zq0N7Hq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZq0N7Hq.png&h=a5f5a57c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後食飽梗係要行下啦，唔通個個都變到肥絲大隻咁撚肥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現推介sell hk旗下既YOHO Mall<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYoHo mall位處於YOHO<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xcHWAP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xcHWAP.png&h=8eeee761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望各位入黎元朗可以食得開心，買得稱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd8b7b2876d4569c071748ea168280a3879d048","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"仆街post錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951b4fa01a73729055a35480dcf63883e28ba66c","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"仆街post錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31f757f3093af13ec537a6d2cee19ac58ffb6f8","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"仆街post錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff12e88f3f5bbd9ecad5c54362faf1285407741","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"大家一齊發掘下元朗好去處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025c2f1bd444831f10f847204319d4fb85f6be2d","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"大家一齊發掘下元朗好去處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54e6706d8e59530102f178086bef5f7b43af634","tid":1364100,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:34.000Z","msg":"有冇得去叫雞？"},{"pid":"74dfac55827e08698080f2408e11dc21a6ffbc62","tid":1364100,"uid":266081,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYCAw8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYCAw8v.png&h=f72bf509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bytravel.cn/view/top10/index4124.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bytravel.cn%2Fview%2Ftop10%2Findex4124.html&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6RnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=853d3b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bytravel.cn/view/top10/index4124.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://wenzhang.16fan.com/a/224025.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwenzhang.16fan.com%2Fa%2F224025.html&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6RnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=31aa57c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wenzhang.16fan.com/a/224025.html</a><br />\n<br />\n周末 (7月27日) 天气好，来一起去元朗郊游，买 ＂老婆饼＂，用微信支付和支付宝还有优惠！<br />\n听说围村很有历史价值，民风纯朴，男女老幼非常好客，真想参观一下，吃吃茶果！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">请在朋友圈转发！记得要中午到！<br />\n欢迎打印旅游资料，发给国内同胞！</span></span>"},{"pid":"324711bf1f5cf1c6bdd75fa5685670fae018c5f9","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:44.000Z","msg":"大家一齊發掘下元朗好去處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774749adaa3c5013ceb9377c7753628157f833d3","tid":1364100,"uid":176112,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5c09d61fac869395b855c078d94bea52bb79e810","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e54e6706d8e59530102f178086bef5f7b43af634","tid":1364100,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:34.000Z","msg":"有冇得去叫雞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"元朗十街，有無聽過？<br />\n不過唔鼓勵<br />\n會生嘢"},{"pid":"3d13fa28747f86ea1d91f16fade5ee0724ed11dc","tid":1364100,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"入yoho，飲愛國喜茶"},{"pid":"662f1976eae46405c2ce3334014b4448a173810b","tid":1364100,"uid":176092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e54e6706d8e59530102f178086bef5f7b43af634","tid":1364100,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:34.000Z","msg":"有冇得去叫雞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"大棠路站對出有雞街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c871b74ecad6d16eaa2b10e74e517b6292cd82d9","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"774749adaa3c5013ceb9377c7753628157f833d3","tid":1364100,"uid":176112,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},"