/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑咗<br />\n個心有無心絞痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa3c9b58eaceb0a75f2e34bc2203ffe3d54e1e7","tid":1364100,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9782ed0ba69bc4110e1b6faa06eabe5a49fb14a0","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"作為一個係元朗土生土長既牛屎仔<br />\n今日想推廣一下元朗既好去處，美食及購物地點<br />\n<br />\n首先，中秋即將來臨，相信好多香港人都想食到好食既月餅，小弟現推介恆香月餅，恆香既月餅比市面上既好好多，好有月餅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟最高紀錄一次過食撚左兩盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />地址係元朗大棠路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhEy3fF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqhEy3fF.png&h=6553412f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二間就係元朗人必食既爽爽醉雞豬扒店，一定要食新鮮雞！好撚滑！豬扒又係好撚有豬扒味，諗起都想食番一打<br />\n地址係YOHO 附近<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zq0N7Hq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZq0N7Hq.png&h=a5f5a57c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後食飽梗係要行下啦，唔通個個都變到肥絲大隻咁撚肥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現推介sell hk旗下既YOHO Mall<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYoHo mall位處於YOHO<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xcHWAP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xcHWAP.png&h=8eeee761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望各位入黎元朗可以食得開心，買得稱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"香港人自己振興香港旅遊業"},{"pid":"8ee6f4e568fd6243986ccc830051b704fa2ff260","tid":1364100,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b31bece78aa22c4412c0a5e5129b9851b8b5a0d","tid":1364100,"uid":23560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:43:29.000Z","msg":"爽爽正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"係正，但無左堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a2528bd7bcfae1de7e34b45719c04a9b2b6d9f","tid":1364100,"uid":47500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>入嚟瘋狂買老婆餅慶祝新元朝立國呀</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8b32f1799dccdb91554009d94e99b5da6e888de1","tid":1364100,"uid":165442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"657cb86325aa12b7c377c548b44793ed267fea93","tid":1364100,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbc398cf7add234edee5caa2609a555af66fa2fe","tid":1364100,"uid":165442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"有冇元朗返送支持者<br />\n去排隊食下都好喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03712e8f5aa5c269e9f85196b2663540d681878d","tid":1364100,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"[長文]人生最重要的選擇題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363571</a>"},{"pid":"2ca85c7f385b63e4b6ee4324d57bd05ce62d3da0","tid":1364100,"uid":20880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:14:25.000Z","msg":"恒香月餅真係未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係食過佢D老婆餅，我唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}